<!-- Poem 1 -->
<div class="col-md-6 fade-in">
    <div class="card-item">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
            <i class="fas fa-feather-alt text-primary me-2"></i>
            <h4 class="mb-0">"Ozymandias"
                <small class="text-muted">— Percy Bysshe Shelley</small>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted fst-italic">I met a traveller from an antique land,<br>
            Who said—"Two vast and trunkless legs of stone<br>
            Stand in the desert..."</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Poem 2 -->
<div class="col-md-6 fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.1s;">
    <div class="card-item">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
            <i class="fas fa-feather-alt text-primary me-2"></i>
            <h4 class="mb-0">"If—"
                <small class="text-muted">— Rudyard Kipling</small>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted fst-italic">If you can keep your head when all about
            you<br>
            Are losing theirs and blaming it on you...</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Poem 3 -->
<div class="col-md-6 fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.2s;">
    <div class="card-item">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
            <i class="fas fa-feather-alt text-primary me-2"></i>
            <h4 class="mb-0">"Do Not Go Gentle into That Good Night"
                <small class="text-muted">— Dylan Thomas</small>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted fst-italic">Do not go gentle into that good night,<br>
            Old age should burn and rave at close of day...</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Poem 4 -->
<div class="col-md-6 fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.3s;">
    <div class="card-item">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
            <i class="fas fa-feather-alt text-primary me-2"></i>
            <h4 class="mb-0">"Annabel Lee"
                <small class="text-muted">— Edgar Allan Poe</small>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted fst-italic">It was many and many a year ago,<br>
            In a kingdom by the sea...</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Poem 5 -->
<div class="col-md-6 fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.4s;">
    <div class="card-item">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
            <i class="fas fa-feather-alt text-primary me-2"></i>
            <h4 class="mb-0">"The Raven"
                <small class="text-muted">— Edgar Allan Poe</small>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted fst-italic">Once upon a midnight dreary, while I pondered,
            weak and
            weary,<br>
            Over many a quaint and curious volume of forgotten lore...</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Poem 6 -->
<div class="col-md-6 fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.5s;">
    <div class="card-item">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
            <i class="fas fa-feather-alt text-primary me-2"></i>
            <h4 class="mb-0">"She Walks in Beauty"
                <small class="text-muted">— Lord Byron</small>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted fst-italic">She walks in beauty, like the night<br>
            Of cloudless climes and starry skies...</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Poem 7 -->
<div class="col-md-6 fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.6s;">
    <div class="card-item">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
            <i class="fas fa-feather-alt text-primary me-2"></i>
            <h4 class="mb-0">"Invictus"
                <small class="text-muted">— William Ernest Henley</small>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted fst-italic">I am the master of my fate,<br>
            I am the captain of my soul.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Poem 8 -->
<div class="col-md-6 fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.7s;">
    <div class="card-item">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
            <i class="fas fa-feather-alt text-primary me-2"></i>
            <h4 class="mb-0">"A Red, Red Rose"
                <small class="text-muted">— Robert Burns</small>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted fst-italic">O my Luve is like a red, red rose<br>
            That’s newly sprung in June...</p>
    </div>
</div>